</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[813,1425,645,1680]" pageId="11" pageNumber="3201">Morphometry: (length in mm). Male: Body 17.15, Tegmina 11.7, Hind femur 10.6, Pronotum 3.7.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[813,1425,645,1680]" pageId="11" pageNumber="3201">Remarks: It is a large species other than those already recorded. It may well become minor pests at times.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[813,1425,645,1680]" pageId="11" pageNumber="3201">Natural enemies: No natural enemies have been recorded.</paragraph>
